                <p class="column">With exciting sessions by community organizers and engaged students.</p> 
            <p class="column">the conference will be a day of learning, skill building and lively discussion.</p>
            <p class="nav_p bg_green">@Html.ActionLink("About", "About", "Home",null,new{title="About Service Speaks"})</p>
